online.game
Class commonPlayer

java.lang.Object
  online.game.commonPlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, CompareTo<commonPlayer>, PlayConstants, Play2Constants
public class commonPlayer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.image.ImageObserver, Play2Constants, CompareTo<commonPlayer>

this class holds information about players. It's used by both the game controller and the game client. Rectangles defined in the player object should be laid out by the game's online.common.exCanvas.setLocalBounds method
